data.description: This well-maintained home boasts wood floors throughout. The open concept living and dining area is tailored for hosting and bringing loved ones together during festive seasons. Upstairs, three comfortable bedrooms and a bathroom offer comfort and convenience. The finished basement offers even more versatility, with an additional room for guest space, a half bath, and abundant space for additional living areas, a gym, or a playroom. This home provides ample room for both creating cherished memories and exploring future possibilities.
